@base-url=http://localhost:9801
@user-api-path=/api/v1/users

### Status
GET {{base-url}}/internal/status

#####

### Create a user - admin
POST {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Nenad",
  "lastName": "Pantelic",
  "username": "npantelija",
  "email": "npant@elic.com",
  "password": "pass123456",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### Create a user - user
POST {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Petar",
  "lastName": "Petrovic",
  "username": "pera_detlich",
  "email": "pera@detlic.com",
  "password": "pass123456",
  "role": "USER"
}


