#####
### List users
GET {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}

### List users - page 1 and size 25
GET {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}?page=1&size=25

#####
### Get user
GET {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}/1

### Get nonexistent user
GET {{base-url}}{{user-api-path}}/1111


#####
